 <p>Cartumandua Spiritslammer
Clan Spiritslammer
"Phat Loot, No Work" - The Druid Motto</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/ualvimar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alvimar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#CC9900>(2/17/01 11:40:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: We need a vote on Phinny</span><hr size=1> Maybe it's just general bi-polar nature Cart.. :^)  I'd think 2 days a week reservable would be smart and still hold Naggy raids should hold a priority... they really don't right now but it's been 'policy' in practice. <p><FONT face="Comic Sans MS" size="2" font color=#8A2BE2>Bristlebane's best to you all,<br>
